Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.60,0:09:15.50,IN_EN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur5}Let it all out
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.70,0:09:19.20,IN_EN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur5}I'm here always
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.10,0:09:24.90,IN_EN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur5}Never will leave your side
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.50,0:09:28.10,IN_EN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur5}Cry on and on
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.50,0:09:33.10,IN_EN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur5}Let those tears come on down
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.50,0:09:37.80,IN_EN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur5}Tomorrow will come again soon
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.75,0:00:27.50,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}對了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.20,0:00:30.20,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}今天是休息日來著
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.56,0:02:07.80,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}跟大家商量過後 決定今天休息一天
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.30,0:02:10.95,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}到昨天為止發生了許多事
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.55,0:02:12.80,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}該怎麼說呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.55,0:02:15.50,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}算是告一段落了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.10,0:02:20.80,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}但這是怎麼回事 有種很奇怪的感覺
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.75,0:02:24.40,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}休息日我都在幹什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.15,0:02:29.35,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}假日啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.35,0:02:30.80,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}怎麼了？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.80,0:02:32.00,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}啊 沒什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.95,0:02:36.30,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}放假反而讓我不知道幹什麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.35,0:02:40.15,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}藍德他很早就出門了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.15,0:02:41.15,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}真的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.15,0:02:42.15,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}真意外
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.70,0:02:46.30,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}是有人會一休息反而起得更早呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.45,0:02:49.30,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}你在說這個啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.60,0:03:01.75,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}這麵包真好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.75,0:03:05.75,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}烤的火候
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.45,0:03:09.50,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我還掌握不太好
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.60,0:03:11.60,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}似乎是在中途改變火的大小就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.15,0:03:13.25,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}但我們用的是柴火
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.25,0:03:14.90,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}休息天就別再燒飯啦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.65,0:03:17.70,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}不是 我是很感激的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.35,0:03:19.35,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}沒事的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.35,0:03:21.63,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}正好我也餓了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.30,0:03:24.65,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}藍德說要去哪？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.35,0:03:26.95,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}他拿著釣竿
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.80,0:03:29.00,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}夢兒和席赫露呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.80,0:03:32.35,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}今天早上還沒看到
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.60,0:03:35.05,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}還在房間裡嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.80,0:03:40.10,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}可能是睡得比較晚吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.05,0:03:43.20,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}席赫露哭得很厲害
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.15,0:03:47.25,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}應該會和夢兒談到馬納多吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.60,0:03:50.50,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}莫古索呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.10,0:03:51.95,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.45,0:03:53.80,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我想想
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.00,0:03:57.05,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}維護一下防具吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.65,0:04:00.15,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}上次那場戰鬥弄壞了不少地方
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.85,0:04:02.20,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}武器也很破
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.20,0:04:03.30,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}拿去打磨了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.05,0:04:06.10,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}要去取回來才行
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.10,0:04:08.30,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}這好像和平時沒什麼兩樣吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.85,0:04:10.35,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}今天可是難得的休息天啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.05,0:04:12.75,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}哈爾希洛要幹什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.65,0:04:14.55,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.55,0:04:15.60,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.50,0:04:21.25,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}傍晚在雪莉的酒館集合對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.20,0:04:23.80,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.30,0:04:31.55,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}怎麼辦呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.85,0:04:38.30,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}席赫露也起來了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.80,0:04:42.30,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}你喜歡鳥嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.95,0:04:45.95,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}習慣了 不知不覺就...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.75,0:04:47.60,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}唔...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.25,0:04:53.10,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}啊 莫古索他
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.20,0:04:55.85,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}烤了新的麵包
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.75,0:04:57.75,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}聞起來很香
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.40,0:04:59.00,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}都飄到這了？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.60,0:05:00.50,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.40,0:05:08.65,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}在這裡 大家有一起看過夕陽
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.80,0:05:17.40,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.67,0:05:21.40,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}那個
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.95,0:05:22.95,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}哈爾希洛
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.15,0:05:25.35,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}今後也請多多關照了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.85,0:05:26.95,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}嗯？怎麼了？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.70,0:05:28.85,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}彼此彼此
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.70,0:05:30.65,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}為什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.10,0:05:32.10,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}順勢就說了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.15,0:05:39.50,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}朝陽也很美哦 從這裡看的話
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.45,0:05:43.35,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.25,0:05:45.70,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}所以才會成為習慣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.25,0:05:48.90,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.05,0:05:53.05,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}席赫露
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.80,0:05:58.05,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}夢兒醒著 起來了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.65,0:07:05.50,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}哈爾
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.40,0:07:12.40,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}坐吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.30,0:07:23.55,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我住在這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.25,0:07:26.30,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}這家旅館裡都是女人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.65,0:07:30.30,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}自從離開義勇兵宿舍以後 就一直住在這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.15,0:07:32.55,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}那麼 這裡也是...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.55,0:07:33.85,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}露台沒事
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.30,0:07:48.20,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}你們要離開宿舍的話
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.00,0:07:51.85,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我可以把這裡介紹給夢兒和席赫露
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.70,0:07:53.30,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.90,0:07:55.45,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}她們兩個應該會高興的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.55,0:07:59.65,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}雖然 我們已經習慣了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.53,0:08:03.90,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}不過總有一天是要離開的 肯定
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.80,0:08:13.50,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}宿舍嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.40,0:08:19.10,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}梅麗住在那個破爛宿舍的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.70,0:08:23.45,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}一定是和他最初的同胞們一起的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.40,0:08:30.05,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}和那些現在已經不在了的同伴們一起
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.60,0:10:14.50,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}呃 達姆洛？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.65,0:10:18.75,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}好像殺氣騰騰呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.75,0:10:20.90,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}那邊的哥布林們
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.90,0:10:24.20,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}嘛 不過我只知道他們殺氣騰騰的樣子
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.20,0:10:25.70,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}你是新來的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.70,0:10:26.80,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}人新
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.80,0:10:27.80,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}人新？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.55,0:10:29.90,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}新人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.90,0:10:31.25,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}見習義勇兵嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.25,0:10:32.60,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}沒錯 就是這個
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.60,0:10:38.85,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}那個人新的隊伍好像很慘哦 在達姆洛
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.85,0:10:40.25,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}很糟哦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.25,0:10:44.20,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我們打倒的那只哥布林應該是從新街區來的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.85,0:10:47.70,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}裝備和動作都高一個檔次
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.40,0:10:49.70,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}因為我們打倒了它...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.70,0:10:51.15,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}沒錯沒錯
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.15,0:10:57.65,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}生氣的哥布林從新街區大量涌入 怒氣沖沖地在巡邏
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.65,0:10:59.80,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}那麼對我們來說呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.80,0:11:01.50,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}暫時不要去管它們
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.50,0:11:03.80,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}該怎麼說呢 熱氣騰騰的蛋糕？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.80,0:11:05.70,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}燙的時候不要去碰啦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.10,0:11:09.20,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}真的假的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.20,0:11:11.00,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}呦呦 還好嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.00,0:11:12.20,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}幹得如何
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.15,0:11:14.55,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}再來兩瓶
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.55,0:11:16.35,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}哥布真慘
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.35,0:11:19.15,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}與其說是哥布林 應該說是達姆洛
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.15,0:11:20.00,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}你聽到了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.50,0:11:20.80,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.80,0:11:22.35,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}要怎麼辦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.35,0:11:23.15,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}什麼怎麼辦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.15,0:11:25.50,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我還沒開始想的 說實話
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.50,0:11:28.90,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}明天本來也打算去達姆洛的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.90,0:11:31.55,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}明天去達姆洛賺不到錢的話
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.70,0:11:33.95,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}哈爾希洛 你可是要負全責的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.95,0:11:35.70,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}什麼責任啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.70,0:11:39.30,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我說讓你戰士點誠意 起碼要把你那份報酬給我
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.30,0:11:41.80,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}為什麼我要做這種事
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.65,0:11:45.70,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}再說了 如果賺不到錢 那報酬也是零啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.60,0:11:49.80,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}那個 換個地方打獵怎麼樣
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.45,0:11:54.70,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}賽琳礦山
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.90,0:12:02.25,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}啊 不 抱歉 我自言自語...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.25,0:12:05.75,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}哈爾希洛 你偶爾也會提點不錯的主意嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.75,0:12:07.60,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}雖說只是偶爾
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.60,0:12:09.55,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我當然舉雙手贊成
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.10,0:12:11.30,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}沒事嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.80,0:12:14.55,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}賽琳礦山不是有Tetra Pot
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.55,0:12:17.15,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}賞金有30金呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.15,0:12:21.25,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}不是Teara Pot 是Dead Spot 還有是賽琳礦山
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.65,0:12:28.00,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}不管怎麼說 眼下只能換地方了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.55,0:12:33.80,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}但是別的地方我完全不認識 現在想該怎麼辦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.90,0:12:39.50,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}只要小心不碰上Dead Spot
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.30,0:12:43.60,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}一直在同一個地方也太千篇一律了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.00,0:12:47.00,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}會變得像日常刷本一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.50,0:12:50.15,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}也可能會因此犯下奇怪的錯誤
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.95,0:12:54.80,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}偶爾還是需要一點刺激和緊張感
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.40,0:13:00.15,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}也是
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.05,0:13:01.80,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.80,0:13:05.80,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}想去賽琳礦山
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.30,0:13:09.55,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}那樣的話
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.95,0:13:11.55,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.40,0:13:15.50,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}每天都一樣就這麼不好嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.35,0:13:18.95,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}最近危險的情況也開始減少了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.45,0:13:21.70,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}錢也一點點存起來了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.55,0:13:24.40,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}夢兒沒有不滿
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.00,0:13:28.55,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}唔..只是達姆洛那邊的情況...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.55,0:13:29.70,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}對哦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.60,0:13:32.55,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}那也沒辦法了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.30,0:13:37.85,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}獵物變了 心情也會變 說不定不錯呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.35,0:13:41.10,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}梅麗？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.55,0:13:56.30,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}稍微
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.80,0:13:57.80,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}失陪一下
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.90,0:13:59.60,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}梅麗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.45,0:15:00.50,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.90,0:15:05.45,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}不 我才是
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.95,0:15:10.80,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}去賽琳礦山
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.40,0:15:16.65,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}梅麗就不得不踏入失去同伴的現場了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.15,0:15:19.35,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}這樣她會很難受
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.15,0:15:21.15,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}非常痛苦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.75,0:15:30.50,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我們在那之後其實也基本沒有接近過 馬納多去世的那個地方
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.20,0:15:36.50,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}連這種地方的存在本身
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.95,0:15:40.60,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}都想要忘記
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.60,0:15:50.00,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}賽琳礦山 去賽琳礦山的話 我高興不起來 應該
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.95,0:15:52.95,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}現在也是
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.95,0:15:56.95,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}大概 今後一直都會是
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.10,0:15:59.90,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}也是
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.55,0:16:05.70,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}但是 這是一定要跨越的坎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.60,0:16:10.00,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}不 是我想跨越
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.50,0:16:12.95,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}不然我就無法前進
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.28,0:16:18.05,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}可是 我一個人是無法跨越的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.50,0:16:22.15,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}要借助別人的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.25,0:16:24.50,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}需要你們
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.85,0:16:28.35,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}跟你們一起去 我會很高興
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.95,0:16:36.45,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}因為你們說我是你們的同伴
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.35,0:16:41.70,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}雖然可能會給你們添麻煩
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.73,0:16:45.35,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}不會麻煩的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.05,0:16:49.55,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}怎麼可能是麻煩呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.50,0:16:55.30,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}哈爾
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.30,0:16:57.30,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}為什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.75,0:17:01.10,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}可能是因為我很開心
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.30,0:17:04.50,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我真遜啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.85,0:17:12.50,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}哈爾這樣就很好了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.70,0:17:21.55,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}謝謝你
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.80,0:17:38.50,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}要去賽琳礦山 必須要做好萬全的準備
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.85,0:17:42.40,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}裝備 還有技能
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.60,0:17:48.00,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我付了40銀 選擇了學習偷襲戰法中的蜘蛛
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.20,0:17:52.65,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}那麼久開始吧 Old Cat
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.65,0:17:53.90,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}請多指教
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.45,0:17:56.75,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}變得這麼僵硬
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.75,0:18:00.30,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}硬的只要有你身上掛著的東西就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.30,0:18:03.70,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}不 那個並不硬...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.80,0:18:09.20,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}實戰的話你的頭和身體就已經拜拜了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.80,0:18:12.90,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}沒有短刀的話折了你的頸椎也不錯
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.10,0:18:19.75,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我先回一直對你使用蜘蛛
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.75,0:18:21.35,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}直到你吐血為止
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.40,0:18:24.10,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}不會死嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.10,0:18:25.45,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}放心吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.00,0:18:30.80,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}在我的訓練下死掉的 至今為止就那幾個人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.80,0:18:32.20,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}哪幾個人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.90,0:18:48.50,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}站不起來了的話就沒辦法了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.50,0:18:49.60,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}休息一會兒吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.10,0:18:53.25,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}休息的時候也要鍛煉哦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.25,0:18:55.40,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}腹肌 腹肌
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.40,0:18:59.05,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}還是說改成忍受拷問的訓練比較好
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.05,0:19:01.15,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}會死的 真的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.15,0:19:03.75,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}那就聊會天吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.35,0:19:05.40,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}不行
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.40,0:19:07.05,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}趕緊聊 笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.55,0:19:10.70,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}聊...聊天
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.70,0:19:12.00,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}小笑話也行
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.00,0:19:14.30,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我想不到這種梗啦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.30,0:19:16.35,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}你還真是個無聊的男人
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.35,0:19:18.50,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}所以才沒女朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.20,0:19:22.50,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}沒...沒法否認
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.50,0:19:24.80,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}你隊伍裡也有女人的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.65,0:19:27.65,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}有...有三個
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.65,0:19:29.20,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}好歹搞上一個
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.25,0:19:33.40,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}不過 全吃了才是王道
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.40,0:19:35.65,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}不 這種事我有點...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.55,0:19:38.85,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}總歸有個在意的女人吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.95,0:19:43.05,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}你剛才是不是想到了誰的臉
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.15,0:19:45.40,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}對...對了老師
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.80,0:19:49.00,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我有事情想跟你商量...問你
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.00,0:19:51.25,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}肯定是跟女人有關吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.25,0:19:53.30,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}不是的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.30,0:19:56.15,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}你是想岔開話題
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.15,0:19:58.95,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我沒那種精力 真的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.15,0:20:05.00,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}原來如此
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.65,0:20:08.05,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}這是個不錯的徵兆
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.05,0:20:09.20,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}徵兆
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.20,0:20:11.70,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}但是 可別誤會了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.70,0:20:13.85,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}這不是什麼特別的事
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.35,0:20:20.30,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}不 什麼誤會不誤會的 我都不知道這是怎麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.30,0:20:22.10,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}真遲鈍
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.10,0:20:24.40,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}你就是只Old Cat
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.40,0:20:25.20,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}遲鈍？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.85,0:20:26.80,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}遲鈍
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.35,0:20:29.80,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}但是直覺卻挺準
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.50,0:20:35.55,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}你看到的線 只要積累經驗每個人都會看到個一兩次
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.20,0:20:41.00,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我的情況是 還沒到一天一次那麼勤 不過也挺多的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.70,0:20:44.25,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}這種情況也有
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.25,0:20:45.80,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}各個人差別很大
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.60,0:20:47.80,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}老師呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.90,0:20:51.40,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}有時看得到有時看不到
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.40,0:20:53.80,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}也不是什麼集中精力就能看到的東西
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.30,0:20:55.20,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我看
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.40,0:20:59.50,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}要提高準確性的話 就要磨練技術
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.50,0:21:00.90,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}還有體力
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.55,0:21:02.75,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}是...是
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.75,0:21:05.75,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}說自己沒精力 就是還差火候
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.75,0:21:26.30,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}看上去只是座山啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.65,0:21:33.70,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}賽琳礦山 是在從前人族的阿拉巴吉亞王國
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.20,0:21:37.45,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}向邊境擴張勢力時開發的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.80,0:21:46.50,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}在無命之王率領的軍勢 驅逐了人族之後 就由地精一派佔領了礦山
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.25,0:21:50.60,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}聽說在那之後 他們就一隻居住在礦山裡
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.15,0:21:53.95,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}好
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.95,0:21:54.75,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}上吧
